node.text: The new album is named for West’s late mother, who passed away in 2007. While DONDA explores a wider range of genres than his previous album Jesus is King, it features some of the religious themes that West has pivoted to in his recent music. A partial tracklist posted by West ahead of the release listed titles like “Pure Souls” and “Keep My Spirit Alive.” The album will be available for purchase and streaming on July 23rd.

node.text: Founded by Jeff Bezos, space travel company Blue Origin completed its first passenger flight on July 20. The rocket, named New Shepard, carried Bezos and three other passengers more than 65-miles above Earth, just to the boundary of space, known as the Kármán line. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to learn more.

node.title: @jeffbezos Completes His First Flight into Space

@hypebeastkicks: In case you missed it, here’s a first look at @kingjames’ latest @nike LeBron 19 in an all-black buildup. node.text:
Popular @cartoonnetworkofficial animated series 'Adventure Time' is getting a spinoff series starring Fionna and Cake. The two characters were originally introduced in the show in 2011, created in the style of the original characters Finn and Jake. The spin-off is set to have 10 episodes and will debut on @hbomax. Currently, there is no set release date for the show.⁠
Photo: Cartoon Network

@hypebeastcarclub: @bmw and @calderfoundation have announced an Artist’s Proof iteration of the Philadelphia-born artist’s 1975 take on the iconic 3.0 CSL. This version is not a “replica, clone, copy, reproduction, facsimile, or 1:1 of the 1975 Calder BMW Art Car. Rather, it is the identical Artist’s Proof that Calder was entitled to but was never realized until now.” Learn more about it via the link in bio.⁠⁠

@hypebeastkicks: @rickowensonline and @converse have reunited for their latest take on the Weapon dubbed the TURBOWPN. Owens has distorted the ’80s silhouette with new design features that exaggerate proportions, including an elongated tongue and a double-sized outsole, a signature Owens design touch. Launching the collaboration, the designer said, “When I discovered how powerful just oversizing something a little bit was, which I’ve done with a lot of my clothes, that became one of my tools.” Expect these to launch on August 31.⁠
Photo: Converse

@hypebeastkicks: @thesocialstatus has officially announced the release dates for its @nike Dunk Mid collaborations, while also debuting a short film dubbed FREE LUNCH to accompany the launches. The visual directed by @dreadheadfilms aims to show the “joy in the struggle" through a story of three brothers on their way to get a free lunch. The “Chocolate Milk” iteration will release on September 4, while the “Strawberry Milk” will drop on September 18. You can also watch the short film via the link in our bio.⁠⁠
